*Provela* je većinu dana u krevetu. (She spent most of the day in bed.)

*Provela* je svoje slobodno vreme u parku. (She spent her free time in the park.)

On je *provela* odmor u inostranstvu. (He spent his vacation abroad.)

*Provode* se više od dva sata u šetnji. (They spent more than two hours walking.)

Oni su *provodili* veče u uživanju. (They spent the evening enjoying.)

*Provodeći* veče zajedno, razgovarali su o budućnosti. (Spending the evening together, they talked about the future.)